sequenceDiagram
    actor Doctor
    participant Episode
    participant AsclenaAI as Asclena AI
    participant Prescription
    actor Patient

    Doctor->>Episode: 1. Review final lab & imaging reports
    Doctor->>AsclenaAI: 2. Request treatment recommendation
    AsclenaAI->>Doctor: 3. Suggest medications, dosage, and plan
    Doctor->>Prescription: 4. Write prescription (medication, dose, frequency, duration)
    Prescription->>Episode: 5. Link prescription to active Episode
    Doctor->>Patient: 6. Explain diagnosis and treatment plan
    Patient->>Doctor: 7. Acknowledge and confirm understanding